  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Petal by Petal</strong> is a relaxing incremental game where a single drop of water can turn into a blooming empire. Forget about stress or game-overs. Experience the vibrant satisfaction of the late game as your screen fills with a <strong>massive array of colours</strong>, rewarding your patience and growth with beautiful visual density.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grow your flowers</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You don't need to click your way to success. Just rest your cursor over a thirsting seed and watch as it drinks up the water, growing in steady, calming intervals. It’s a game designed to respect your hand and your peace of mind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As your garden expands, you won't have to tend to every seed alone. Invest your earnings in high-grade sprinkler systems for constant care, or unlock the power of the sky to summon gentle rain clouds, ensuring every flower blooms even when your hands are off the mouse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4223140/extras/2bc38ad6ad1884b7b0621cddcc69f961.poster.avif?t=1773788182\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4223140/extras/2bc38ad6ad1884b7b0621cddcc69f961.webm?t=1773788182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4223140/extras/2bc38ad6ad1884b7b0621cddcc69f961.mp4?t=1773788182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover Flowers With Unique Abilities</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover and unlock a wide encyclopaedia of flora. From common sunflowers to rare, exotic orchids that yield high rewards, every new seed offers a fresh splash of colour for your screen along with unique abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4223140/extras/e5d3d3e201932ba73cda8550ae8e01d2.poster.avif?t=1773788182\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4223140/extras/e5d3d3e201932ba73cda8550ae8e01d2.webm?t=1773788182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4223140/extras/e5d3d3e201932ba73cda8550ae8e01d2.mp4?t=1773788182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock upgrades</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Invest your earnings into better tools, special abilities, and automated hydration systems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4223140/extras/83af650d06fc68d74a18cc095f4ffac9.poster.avif?t=1773788182\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4223140/extras/83af650d06fc68d74a18cc095f4ffac9.webm?t=1773788182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4223140/extras/83af650d06fc68d74a18cc095f4ffac9.mp4?t=1773788182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Light and dark mode</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soft colours, gentle swaying and chill music create a zen-like atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4223140/extras/50b2eec737a867e8446695c2dce0ed41.poster.avif?t=1773788182\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4223140/extras/50b2eec737a867e8446695c2dce0ed41.webm?t=1773788182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4223140/extras/50b2eec737a867e8446695c2dce0ed41.mp4?t=1773788182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow a tiny seed into a screen-filling garden of colour</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock 200+ upgrades across multiple upgrade trees</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover flowers with unique abilities and behaviours</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Automate your garden with sprinklers, rain clouds and more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax with gentle animations, soft colours and chill music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple modes including Calm Mode or Garden for stress-free play </p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Petal by Petal</strong> is a relaxing incremental game where a single drop of water can turn into a blooming empire. Forget about stress or game-overs. Experience the vibrant satisfaction of the late game as your screen fills with a <strong>massive array of colours</strong>, rewarding your patience and growth with beautiful visual density.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grow your flowers</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You don't need to click your way to success. Just rest your cursor over a thirsting seed and watch as it drinks up the water, growing in steady, calming intervals. It’s a game designed to respect your hand and your peace of mind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As your garden expands, you won't have to tend to every seed alone. Invest your earnings in high-grade sprinkler systems for constant care, or unlock the power of the sky to summon gentle rain clouds, ensuring every flower blooms even when your hands are off the mouse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4223140/extras/2bc38ad6ad1884b7b0621cddcc69f961.poster.avif?t=1773788182\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4223140/extras/2bc38ad6ad1884b7b0621cddcc69f961.webm?t=1773788182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4223140/extras/2bc38ad6ad1884b7b0621cddcc69f961.mp4?t=1773788182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover Flowers With Unique Abilities</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover and unlock a wide encyclopaedia of flora. From common sunflowers to rare, exotic orchids that yield high rewards, every new seed offers a fresh splash of colour for you