tps://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4223140/extras/50b2eec737a867e8446695c2dce0ed41.webm?t=1773788182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4223140/extras/50b2eec737a867e8446695c2dce0ed41.mp4?t=1773788182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow a tiny seed into a screen-filling garden of colour</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock 200+ upgrades across multiple upgrade trees</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover flowers with unique abilities and behaviours</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Automate your garden with sprinklers, rain clouds and more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax with gentle animations, soft colours and chill music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple modes including Calm Mode or Garden for stress-free play </p></li></ul>",
